{"article_id":"KPAL6a9GbbnutCCD","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump steps off Air Force One upon arrival at Andrews Air Force Base in Maryland on December 2 , 2017 .","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"President Donald Trump had been unusually quiet on Twitter about the bombshell news","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that his former national security adviser , Michael Flynn , had pleaded guilty to lying to the FBI about his communications with Russian officials .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"That changed on Saturday ,","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"when Trump took to his favorite social media outlet","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to say","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"Flynn had \" nothing to hide. \"","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"But","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"in doing so ,","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"Trump may have admitted to something","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"that could get him in trouble in the future","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"because his tweet suggested","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"he knew","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"Flynn had lied to the FBI","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"when he fired him .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"\" I had to fire General Flynn","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"because he lied to the Vice President and the FBI , \"","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"\" He has pled guilty to those lies .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"It is a shame","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"because his actions during the transition were lawful .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"There was nothing to hide !","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"\" I had to fire General Flynn","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"because he lied to the Vice President and the FBI .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"He has pled guilty to those lies .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"It is a shame","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"because his actions during the transition were lawful .","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"There was nothing to hide !","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"December 2 , 2017","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"The first part of the tweet immediately raised eyebrows .","depth":5},{"id":32,"text":"Why ?","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"Because it would suggest","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Trump knew more about Flynn ' s lies","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"than what he has said publicly .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"When Trump fired Flynn on Feb. 13","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"he only said","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"it was because his then-national security adviser had lied to Vice President Mike Pence about his contacts with Russian officials .","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"The Washington Post revealed news","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"that Flynn had lied to the FBI","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"as well three days after he was fired .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"More importantly though , it would suggest","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Trump knew","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"that Flynn had lied to the FBI","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"when he asked then-FBI chief James Comey to go easy on Flynn on Feb. 14 .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"That is at least what Comey told Congress in June . \"","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"The President then returned to the topic of Mike Flynn ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"saying ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"' He is a good guy","depth":12},{"id":50,"text":"and has been through a lot ' , \"","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"Comey said in his written testimony to Congress .","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"\" He repeated","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"that Flynn hadn ' t done anything wrong on his calls with the Russians ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"but had misled the Vice President .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"He then said ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"' I hope","depth":13},{"id":57,"text":"you can see your way clear to letting this go , to letting Flynn go .","depth":13},{"id":58,"text":"He is a good guy .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"I hope","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"you can let this go ' . \"","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"The Washington Post is reporting","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that it was Trump ' s lawyer , John Dowd , who drafted the tweet and not the president himself .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"The Post explains","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"why that ' s important :","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"Its authorship could reduce how significantly it communicates anything","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"about when the president knew","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"that Flynn had lied to the FBI ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"but also raises questions about the public relations strategy of the president ' s chief lawyer .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Two people close to the administration described the tweet simply as sloppy and unfortunate .","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"That revelation though didn ' t stop critics from questioning","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"how much Trump knew about Flynn ' s lies to the FBI","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"and whether he tried to obstruct justice .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"\" If that is true ,","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"Mr. President ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"why did you wait so long to fire Flynn ? \"","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"asked Rep. Adam Schiff in a tweet .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"\" Why did you fail to act","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"until his lies were publicly exposed ?","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"And why did you pressure Director Comey to \" let this go ? \"","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"If that is true ,","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Mr. President ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"why did you wait so long to fire Flynn ?","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Why did you fail to act","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"until his lies were publicly exposed ?","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"And why did you pressure Director Comey to \" let this go ? \"","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"https : //t.co/Ea4kOBpWPv","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"- Adam Schiff","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"( @ RepAdamSchiff )","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"December 2 , 2017","depth":6},{"id":90,"text":"Rep. Ted Lieu of California was even more direct","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"and apparently couldn ' t contain his shock ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"deciding to tweet","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"using capital letters :","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"\" THIS IS OBSTRUCTION OF JUSTICE , \"","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"he wrote .","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"THIS IS OBSTRUCTION OF JUSTICE .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"@ POTUS now admits","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"he KNEW","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"Michael Flynn lied to the FBI .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Yet Trump tried to influence or stop the FBI investigation on # Flynn .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"https : //t.co/8JqGBxgou0","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"- Ted Lieu","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"( @ tedlieu )","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"December 2 , 2017","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"Walter Shaub , the former head of the U.S. Office of Government Ethics , flat out said","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"that any other president could have lost his job over the tweet .","depth":6},{"id":107,"text":"\" Before we slipped into an alternate universe of unabashed corruption ,","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"this tweet alone might have ended a Presidential administration , \"","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"Shaub wrote .","depth":6}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":0,"right":218,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":218,"left":169,"right":217,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":169,"left":139,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":130,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":115,"right":129,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":115,"left":111,"right":114,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":111,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"